description:
This is an outfit set for Loid, Anya, Yor, and Bond to use in SPY×ANYA: Operation Memories.

Excited Outfit Pack
 • Denim Set
    - Loid's Peanut T-shirt & Jeans
    - Anya and Yor's Overalls
    - Bond's Denim Bow
• Punk Set
    - Loid, Anya, and Yor's Punk Outfit
    - Bond's Punk Collar
• In-Game Bonus Items:
    - Penguin Statue (Earn 2x PP)
    - 10,000 PP

*Please note that contents are included in the Deluxe Edtion and Deluxe Outing Pack. Please be mindful of duplicate purchases.
*Custom outfits will not be displayed during certain minigames and cutscenes.
name: SPY×ANYA: Operation Memories - Excited Outifit Pack
